          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Factorization (dgeqrf): 2*m*n*k - 2*k^3/3, k = min(m, n)\n(G&VL 4e \u00a75.2). Modes \"reduced\"/\"complete\" additionally form Q\nexplicitly (dorgqr), modeled as the same count again. Modes\n\"r\"/\"raw\" bill the factorization only."
            }
